WEBVTT

1
01:40:14.850 --> 01:40:16.260 
-不  -是的
- No. - Yes.

2
01:40:17.140 --> 01:40:21.390 
在内疚  悔恨和自责中慢慢消亡
In a long, slow degradation of guilt and regret and blame.

3
