胡说
That is nonsense.

4
01:40:26.270 --> 01:40:27.530 
是真相
Truth.

5
01:40:28.730 --> 01:40:30.490 
从矛盾中的出的真相
Made from contradiction.

6
01:40:34.070 --> 01:40:36.450 
